nday, according to separate people with knowledge of the matter.=C2=A0</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">That=E2=80=99s basically a bet=C2=A0that you c=
an get someone (a court, a government) to second-guess the Swiss authoritie=
s=E2=80=99 decision to zero the AT1. The market odds on that bet are betwee=
n 20-to-1 and 50-to-1, so a long shot but not utterly hopeless.</p>
