ew competitor, the people said.=C2=A0</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">All this means Klein=E2=80=99s dream of leadin=
g a new investment bank under the revived CS First Boston brand looks incre=
asingly unlikely.</p>
</blockquote>
