ryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; =
text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-c=
olor: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> US ban=
king regulators issued</a> a =E2=80=9Cjoint statement on liquidity risks re=
sulting from crypto-asset market vulnerabilities,=E2=80=9D warning banks th=
at if they took crypto deposits they would be more vulnerable to a bank run=
. Then there was a series of bank runs and a global banking crisis. Who wou=
ld want those crypto deposits now?</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Meanwhile there <a href=3D"https://link.mail.b=
loombergbusiness.com/click/30911506.258434/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cucmV1dGVycy5jb20v=
YnVzaW5lc3MvZmluYW5jZS9mZGljLWV4dGVuZHMtYmlkZGluZy13aW5kb3ctc3ZiLXNlZWtzLXN=
