240e879d" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" =
style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-wi=
dth: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; backgro=
und-color: #ccc;"> seems to be no buyer</a> for all of Silicon Valley Bank,=
 but there is <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/3091=
1506.258434/aHR0cHM6Ly9uZXdzLmJsb29tYmVyZ2xhdy5jb20vbWVyZ2Vycy1hbmQtYWNxdWl=
